    public class StyleImpl
extends StyleContainerImpl
implements Style
    An implementation of the model object 'Style'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Background
    • Foreground
    • Line Width
    • Line Style
    • Filled
    • Line Visible
    • Rendering Style
    • Transparency
    • Id
    • Description
    • Font
    • Horizontal Alignment
    • Vertical Alignment
    • Angle
    • Stretch H
    • Stretch V
    • Proportional
    • Style Container
    • Rotation
